'''Shalun Station''' ({{zh|t=<U+6C99><U+5D19><U+8ECA><U+7AD9>|p=Sh<U+0101>l<U+00FA>n ch<U+0113>zh<U+00E0>n}}) is a railway station currently under construction on the planned [[Taiwan Railway Administration]] [[Shalun Line]] in [[Guiren, Tainan|Guiren]], [[Tainan County]], [[Taiwan]]. It will connect to the [[THSR Tainan Station|Tainan High Speed Rail Station]].
